overview: The Renegade Galaxy Warrior seeks for a Greater Power to Destroy ALL Life in Space, Moon Central/ City Dome recruits a Useless Bum Civilian who thinks He doesn't have no Future, Now Chosen and Enhanced Fox Alec Holliday is a Force of Nature to Renegade Galaxy Warrior AKA Motu Ko and the Invader Raiders to Enforce the Galaxy.
title: Galaxy-Enforcer 3000
